WANT TO GET A LITTLE WET?

00:00:16.515 --> 00:00:18.417
OKAY, A LOT WET.

00:00:18.618 --> 00:00:20.854
HIT THE SPLASH ZONES.

00:00:21.020 --> 00:00:23.890
OR SLIDE INTO THE WATERY
WORLD OF THE MICKEY POOL.

00:00:24.090 --> 00:00:28.061
THE COOLEST HOTSPOT ON
DECK, JUST FOR KIDS.

00:00:29.862 --> 00:00:32.331
THEN, DRY OFF AND CATCH
UP WITH YOUR DISNEY PALS

00:00:32.532 --> 00:00:34.800
FOR MORE FUN IN THE SUN.

00:00:34.967 --> 00:00:37.002
AND THAT'S JUST
THE BEGINNING.

