EVER WONDER
WHAT'S IN FLUBBER?

00:00:42.941 --> 00:00:45.644
WHAT'S IT LIKE TO CAPTAIN
YOUR OWN PIRATE SHIP?

00:00:45.845 --> 00:00:51.417
OR WHAT TO DO WHEN A REAL
DISNEY PRINCESS POPS
BY FOR STORY TIME?

00:00:51.617 --> 00:00:54.253
EACH DAY, KID CRUISERS
FIND OUT AS THEY MAKE NEW

00:00:54.454 --> 00:00:57.290
FRIENDS AND DISCOVER NEW
WORLDS OF WONDER IN THE

00:00:57.490 --> 00:01:00.894
MOST MAGICAL KID'S
AREAS ON THE SEA.

00:01:01.094 --> 00:01:04.230
MORNING 'TIL MIDNIGHT, A
HOST OF DISNEY COUNSELORS

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:10.003
KEEP THEM ALL SAILING ON
OCEANS OF IMAGINATION.

00:01:10.203 --> 00:01:12.638
KIDS FROM 3 TO 7 ARE
ALL INVITED TO PLAY WITH

00:01:12.838 --> 00:01:16.509
OTHERS THEIR OWN AGE IN
DISNEY'S OCEANEER CLUB,

00:01:16.709 --> 00:01:19.812
