COMES COMPLETE WITH PIXIE DUST

00:01:19.979 --> 00:01:24.583
AND ONE VERY
COOL PIRATE SHIP.

00:01:24.884 --> 00:01:27.353
KIDS 8 TO 12 EMBARK
ON THEIR OWN AMAZING

00:01:27.553 --> 00:01:31.124
ADVENTURES IN
THE OCEANEER LAB.

