HERE, THE EXPERIMENTS GET
A LITTLE GOOEY AND THE

00:01:34.694 --> 00:01:37.796
KIDS GET A LITTLE GOOFY
WITH GADGETS, GIZMOS AND

00:01:37.996 --> 00:01:40.666
ALL KINDS OF
INTERACTIVE GAMES.

00:01:40.866 --> 00:01:43.602
THE CLUB AND THE LAB MAKE
UP NEARLY HALF A DECK

00:01:43.802 --> 00:01:46.205
FILLED WITH THE STUFF
KIDS DREAM ABOUT.

00:01:46.372 --> 00:01:50.008
AND IT'S ALL INCLUDED
WITH YOUR CRUISE.

00:01:50.209 --> 00:01:52.845
MOM AND DAD EVEN GET A
PAGER, SO WHILE THEY'RE

