GOOFY PAJAMA PARTY PACKED
WITH LAUGHTER

00:02:48.101 --> 00:02:54.540
AND ENJOY DAY AFTER DAY OF FUN
CREATED JUST FOR KIDS.

00:02:54.707 --> 00:02:57.210
WHICHEVER DISNEY CRUISE
YOU CHOOSE, KIDS WILL SET

